                    <span>A book that has travelled with me for years and well worth all the space in my limited luggage space. I would definitely take this book to a desert island and it would be a book that I would grab off its shelf if my house was on fire.<P>Time has made me appreciate the voices contained within its cover greatly.</span>
                  
